== PPMC Learning Path

Each podling has its own Project Management Committee (PPMC).  
This path supports new members of a PPMC.

[.small]
*Key:* 📘 Guide 🖥️ Slide Deck 🎞️ Video 🧩 Quiz 🧠 Practice / Scenario

== Steps

1. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+PPMC+Onboarding[Podling PPMC Onboarding] — overview of PPMC responsibilities and expectations  
2. 📘 **Read:** link:https://incubator.apache.org/guides/ppmc.html[Podling Project Management Committee (PPMC) Guide] — official Incubator guidance on PPMC roles and operations  
3. 🖥️ **Slide deck:** link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/PPMC/index.html[PPMC Onboarding] — presentation introducing the role of the PPMC and key governance topics  
4. 🎞️ **Watch:** link:https://youtu.be/yvlasJxYUTs[PPMC Onboarding] — video of PPMC Onboarding presentation  
5. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Governance+in+Practice[Governance in Practice] — applying ASF governance principles in podling decision-making  
6. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Voting+and+Consensus+in+Practice[Voting and Consensus in Practice] — how consensus and voting work within ASF podlings  

